'''黃慧文''' {{post-nominals|country=CAN|MPP}}（{{lang|en|Kristyn Wong-Tam}}，{{bd|1971年|||}}），[[加拿大|加拿大]]政治人物，2022年起以[[安大略新民主黨|安大略新民主黨]]黨員身份任職[[安大略省議會|安大略省議會]]多倫多中選區議員。在此之前她曾活躍於[[多倫多|多倫多]]市級政治，2010年-22年間出任[[多倫多市議會|多倫多市議會]]議員，代表該市的多倫多中選區（第13號市選區；2018年市選前為第27號市選區）。

==早年生活和事業==
黃慧文生於[[香港|香港]]，為家中三名女兒的長女，一家信奉佛教<ref name="TL120314"/><ref>[http://www.torontosun.com/news/torontovotes2010/2010/10/25/15825146.html "Wong-Tam replaces Kyle Rae in Ward 27"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.torontosun.com/news/torontovotes2010/2010/10/25/15825146.html |date=20170912191706 }}. ''Toronto Sun'', October 25, 2010.</ref><ref>[https://www.thestar.com/news/torontocouncil/article/896319--city-hall-rookies-2010-kristyn-wong-tam "City hall rookies 2010: Kristyn Wong-Tam"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.thestar.com/news/torontocouncil/article/896319--city-hall-rookies-2010-kristyn-wong-tam |date=20121023021059 }} ''Toronto Star'', November 24, 2010.</ref>。1975年舉家遷居[[加拿大|加拿大]]，落戶[[多倫多|多倫多]]的{{link-en|麗晶園|Regent Park}}社區，母親在製衣廠工作，父親則在[[蒙特婁|蒙特婁]]的伊利沙伯女王酒店任職廚師，每周末回多倫多與家人團聚<ref name="TL120314"/><ref name=raised>[http://www.blogto.com/people/2011/02/toronto_through_the_eyes_of_councillor_kristyn_wong-tam_/ "Toronto through the eyes of Councillor Kristyn Wong-Tam"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111013140028/http://www.blogto.com/people/2011/02/toronto_through_the_eyes_of_councillor_kristyn_wong-tam_/ |date=2011-10-13 }}.''BlogTO'',February 7, 2011.</ref>。她16歲向家人[[出櫃|出櫃]]後與父母離異，寄居友人住所和庇護所，往後年間逐漸與父母和解<ref name="TL120314"/><ref name=out>[http://www.xtra.ca/public/National/Parental_guidance-3187.aspx "Parental Guidance: Pride 2007 honoured groups/PFLAG Toronto sticks up for queer kids] {{Wayback|url=http://www.xtra.ca/public/National/Parental_guidance-3187.aspx |date=20120928214305 }}. ''Xtra!'', June 21, 2007.</ref>。

她從河谷高中畢業後先到[[約克大學_(加拿大)|約克大學]]主修東亞研究學，期間在兩間庇護所工作，並為同性戀青年外展項目擔當義工<ref name="TL120314"/>。她其後轉到[[多倫多大學|多倫多大學]]修讀，但沒有完成學位<ref name="TL120314"/>。輟學後她熱衷於女權主義，在其英文姓名中加上母親的譚姓<ref name="TL120314"/>。她也積極參與[[LGBTQ|LGBTQ]]和亞裔社區活動，成為多倫多男女同性戀青年組織的共同協調員，曾任{{le|平權會|Chinese Canadian National Council}}多倫多分會會長，並參與成立亞裔加拿大人支持婚姻平權組織<ref name="Xtra101006"/><ref name="TL120314"/><ref name="中評100914">{{cite web | url=http://hk.crntt.com/doc/1014/4/5/7/101445781.html?coluid=49&kindid=972&docid=101445781&mdate=0914105621 | publisher=中評社（取材自《明報》） | title=角逐多倫多市議員 華人黃慧文競選辦公室啟用 | accessdate=2020-11-12 | date=2010-09-14 | archive-date=2020-11-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112200433/http://hk.crntt.com/doc/1014/4/5/7/101445781.html?coluid=49&kindid=972&docid=101445781&mdate=0914105621 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="CityTObio"/>。

她取得地產經紀牌照後加入{{le|科威|Coldwell Banker|科威房產}}，兩年後勝任其多倫多市中心辦事處經理，再於2000年購入位於多倫多同志村的{{le|蒂莫西咖啡館|Timothy's}}特許經營分店<ref name="Xtra101006"/><ref name="TL120314"/>。此後她有感多倫多同志村需成立商業促進會以確立當地形象並對外推廣；經歷兩年拉攏當地商戶支持，{{link-en|教堂街夾韋斯里|Church and Wellesley}}商業促進區終在2002年成立，她亦出任創會成員<ref name="Xtra101006"/><ref name="TL120314"/><ref name="中評100914"/>。她其後出售咖啡店，2004年起在市内營運畫廊<ref name="Xtra101006"/><ref name="TL120314"/><ref name=gallery1>[http://m.theglobeandmail.com/news/arts/rm-vaughan/kristyn-wong-tam-juggling-city-hall-and-an-art-gallery/article1904001/?service=mobile "Kristyn Wong-Tam: Juggling city hall and an art gallery"] {{Wayback|url=http://m.theglobeandmail.com/news/arts/rm-vaughan/kristyn-wong-tam-juggling-city-hall-and-an-art-gallery/article1904001/?service=mobile |date=20120328062712 }}. ''The Globe and Mail'', February 11, 2011.</ref>，後獲邀加入時任多倫多市長[[苗大衛|苗大衛]]成立的經濟競爭力顧問委員會<ref name="CityTObio">{{cite web | url=https://www.toronto.ca/city-government/council/members-of-council/councillor-ward-13/ | publisher=多倫多市政府 | title=Councillor Kristyn Wong-Tam | accessdate=2020-11-13 | archive-date=2021-03-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302071845/https://www.toronto.ca/city-government/council/members-of-council/councillor-ward-13/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==從政==
2008年，時任多倫多市議員[[羅柏特·福特|羅柏特·福特]]在[[多倫多市議會|市議會]]一場有關允許商戶在節假日營業的辯論中發言，指「東方人如狗般工作」和「東方人，他們正在慢慢接管」<ref name="TL120314"/>{{noteTag|name=Ford|1=原文為：「Those Oriental people work like dogs.」和「...the Oriental people, they're slowly taking over.」}}。黃慧文有感這番言論充斥[[族群刻板印象|族群刻板印象]]並具有排外性質，遂要求福特致歉，並率領亞裔示威者到[[多倫多市政廳|多倫多市政廳]]請願<ref name="TL120314"/>。此後黃慧文漸生競選公職的念頭，並於2010年多倫多市選中競逐多倫多中—玫瑰谷選區（第27號市選區）的市議員席位<ref name="TL120314"/><ref name="中評100914"/>，獲得多倫多與約克勞工議會和第20區市議員[[魏德方|魏德方]]等組織和個人支持<ref>[https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/toronto/inside-city-hall/reading-the-labour-council-tea-leaves/article1641147/ "Reading the Labour Council tea leaves"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/toronto/inside-city-hall/reading-the-labour-council-tea-leaves/article1641147/ |date=20140307102240 }}. ''The Globe and Mail'', July 15, 2010.</ref><ref name=nowcand>[http://www.nowtoronto.com/guides/voteto/2010/story.cfm?content=176552 "Rating the races"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nowtoronto.com/guides/voteto/2010/story.cfm?content=176552 |date=20140930152856 }}, ''Now Magazine'', September 2–9</ref>。黃慧文最終僅以400多票之差險勝得票第二高的鄭永強（{{lang|en|Ken Chan}}），首度晉身市議會<ref name=victory>[https://www.thestar.com/news/article/881056--kristyn-wong-tam-replaces-kyle-rae-in-diverse-downtown-riding?bn=1 "Kristyn Wong-Tam replaces Kyle Rae in diverse downtown riding"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.thestar.com/news/article/881056--kristyn-wong-tam-replaces-kyle-rae-in-diverse-downtown-riding?bn=1 |date=20121022155654 }}. ''Toronto Star'', October 25, 2010.</ref><ref name="gallery2">[http://www.torontostandard.com/the-sprawl/the-arrival-of-kristyn-wong-tam "Inside City Hall: The Arrival of Kristyn Wong-Tam"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.torontostandard.com/the-sprawl/the-arrival-of-kristyn-wong-tam |date=20180629235638 }}. ''Toronto Standard'', July 25, 2010.</ref><ref name="raised"/>。

福特在該屆市選改為競逐市長並當選，黃慧文選後表示期待與他合作<ref>''Toronto Sun'', Dec. 3, 2010, p. 6 "Kristyn Wong Tam" by Don Peat</ref>。福特就任市長後兌現競選承諾，取消由市府徵收的車輛登記税，獲得黃慧文支持，但她其後表示後悔支持該項動議<ref name="TL120314"/>。她在首屆市議員任期中與[[央街|央街]]沿線商戶和業主，以及[[懷雅遜大學|懷雅遜大學]]和市中心央街商業促進會共同研制重振央街藍圖，期望透過擴闊行人路和吸引高質零售商店等舉措，提升介乎[[登打士街_(安大略省)|登打士街]]和芝蘭街（{{lang|en|Gerrard Street}}）之間一段央街的吸引力<ref>{{cite web | url=https://torontolife.com/real-estate/yonge-street-revitalization/ | publisher=Toronto Life | title=Kristyn Wong-Tam is pushing an ambitious revitalization plan for Yonge Street—but will it fly at Rob Ford's city hall? | first=Matt | last=Elliott | accessdate=2020-11-25 | date=2011-07-05 | archive-date=2021-03-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303124414/https://torontolife.com/real-estate/yonge-street-revitalization/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。她又與市議員迪貝雷梅（{{lang|en|Glenn De Baeremaeker}}）聯手提出動議，禁止在市内販賣和藏有[[魚翅|魚翅]]，2011年10月獲市議會通過<ref>{{cite web| url=https://www.toronto.com/news-story/65226-councillor-wong-tam-joins-call-for-shark-fin-ban-in-toronto/ | publisher=''East York Mirror'' | title=Councillor Wong-Tam joins call for shark fin ban in Toronto | accessdate=2020-11-25 | date=2011-06-13 | first=David | last=Nickle }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/toronto/toronto-bans-shark-fin-1.1018640 | publisher=CBC News | title=Toronto bans shark fin | accessdate=2020-11-25 | date=2011-10-25 | archive-date=2021-02-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228094534/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/toronto/toronto-bans-shark-fin-1.1018640 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。她於2014年市選中以62%得票率連任第27區市議員<ref name=Reelection>{{cite web|last1=Demara|first1=Bruce|title=Kristyn Wong-Tam easily wins Ward 27, Toronto Centre-Rosedale|url=https://www.thestar.com/news/city_hall/toronto2014election/2014/10/27/toronto_centrerosedale_kristyn_wongtam_easily_wins_ward_27.html|website=Toronto Star|accessdate=26 April 2015|date=27 October 2014|archive-date=2018-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180629155400/https://www.thestar.com/news/city_hall/toronto2014election/2014/10/27/toronto_centrerosedale_kristyn_wongtam_easily_wins_ward_27.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url=http://www1.toronto.ca/City%20Of%20Toronto/City%20Clerks/Elections/Library/Files/Results%20PDFs/2014%20Election/2014clerksofficialdeclarationofresults.pdf#page8| website=Toronto City Council| date=October 30, 2014| title=Declaration of Results| author=Ulli S. Watkiss| access-date=November 6, 2017| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160705235228/http://www1.toronto.ca/City%20Of%20Toronto/City%20Clerks/Elections/Library/Files/Results%20PDFs/2014%20Election/2014clerksofficialdeclarationofresults.pdf#page8| archive-date=July 5, 2016}}</ref>。

2018年市選前，多倫多原計劃將市議會議席數目從44席增至47席<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thestar.com/news/city_hall/2017/12/13/omb-approves-47-wards-for-toronto-for-the-2018-election.html|title=Three seats being added to Toronto council for the 2018 election {{!}} The Star|website=thestar.com|language=en|access-date=2019-01-03|archive-date=2021-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228075317/https://www.thestar.com/news/city_hall/2017/12/13/omb-approves-47-wards-for-toronto-for-the-2018-election.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但[[安大略進步保守黨|安大略進步保守黨]]籍[[安大略省省長|省長]][[道格·福特|道格·福特]]領導下的省政府則通過縮小市議會規模，議席數目減至25席。黃慧文強烈批評此舉，指權力集中不會提升政府質素，又謂此舉侵蝕民主進程<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/toronto/doug-ford-toronto-city-council-cuts-1.4763757|title=Ontario will introduce legislation to slash Toronto city council — a move not welcomed by some|date=2018-07-27|publisher=CBC News|language=en|accessdate=2019-01-03|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411045303/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/toronto/doug-ford-toronto-city-council-cuts-1.4763757|dead-url=no}}</ref>。黃慧文最終在該屆市選競逐重新劃分的多倫多中選區（第13號市選區）市議會議席，並大幅拋離得票第二的前安省內閣廳長[[史振民|史振民]]，以過半得票連任市議員<ref name="wong">{{cite news |title='Incredibly grateful' Kristyn Wong-Tam re-elected in Ward 13, Toronto Centre |url=https://www.thestar.com/news/toronto-election/2018/10/22/easy-win-for-incredibly-grateful-wong-tam-in-ward-13-toronto-centre.html |accessdate=October 23, 2018 |work=Toronto Star |date=October 22, 2018 |archive-date=2019-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190410214822/https://www.thestar.com/news/toronto-election/2018/10/22/easy-win-for-incredibly-grateful-wong-tam-in-ward-13-toronto-centre.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.singtao.ca/toronto/3424505/2018-10-23/post-%E7%8D%A8%E5%BE%9713%E5%8D%80%E9%81%8E%E5%8D%8A%E9%81%B8%E7%A5%A8-%E9%BB%83%E6%85%A7%E6%96%87%E9%80%A3%E4%BB%BB%E5%B8%82%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1/?variant=zh-hk | title=獨得13區過半選票 黃慧文連任市議員 | date=2018-10-23 | publisher=《星島日報》 | accessdate=2019-02-08 | author=脫立新 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190209181826/http://www.singtao.ca/toronto/3424505/2018-10-23/post-%E7%8D%A8%E5%BE%9713%E5%8D%80%E9%81%8E%E5%8D%8A%E9%81%B8%E7%A5%A8-%E9%BB%83%E6%85%A7%E6%96%87%E9%80%A3%E4%BB%BB%E5%B8%82%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1/?variant=zh-hk | archive-date=2019-02-09 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。她於2019年表示市議員總數雖然縮減，但每個市選區的面積相應擴大，增添每名市議員的工作量，並需增聘工作人員服務選區，因此市府最終節省的金額相對整體預算微不足道<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.singtao.ca/3728451/2019-09-01/post-%e8%85%b0%e6%96%ac%e5%a4%9a%e5%b8%82%e8%ad%b0%e5%b8%ad%e6%83%b9%e6%b0%91%e6%80%a8-%e9%96%8b%e6%94%af%e6%9c%aa%e5%a4%a7%e6%b8%9b%e6%9b%b4%e7%84%a1%e6%95%88%e7%8e%87-2/ | title=腰斬多市議席惹民怨 開支未大減更無效率 | date=2019-09-01 | publisher=《星島日報》 | accessdate=2020-11-26 }}</ref>。

2020年[[2019冠狀病毒病加拿大疫情|冠狀病毒疫情]]期間，黃慧文曾建議市府將[[多倫多市中心|市中心]]一段央街改為[[行人專用區|行人專用區]]，以便民眾[[保持人身距離|保持人身距離]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/toronto/kristyn-wong-tam-closing-down-some-streets-1.5507673|title=City councillor proposes closing Yonge Street to traffic to help with social distancing|date=2020-03-24|publisher=CBC News|language=en|accessdate=2020-11-26|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128020444/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/toronto/kristyn-wong-tam-closing-down-some-streets-1.5507673|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2022年4月8日，她宣布將於[[2022年安大略省大選|同年省選]]中代表[[安大略新民主黨|安大略新民主黨]]競逐[[安大略省議會|省議會]]多倫多中選區議席<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.mingpaocanada.com/tor/htm/News/20220409/tgd1_r.htm | title=黃慧文將代表NDP角逐市中心省議席 | date=2022-04-09 | publisher=《明報》加東網 | accessdate=2022-04-21 }}</ref>，並於同年5月4日卸任市議員職務<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://globalnews.ca/news/8745543/kristyn-wong-tam-toronto-centre/|title=Kristyn Wong-Tam resigning from Toronto city council, running as Ontario NDP candidate|date=2022-04-08|publisher=Global News|language=en|accessdate=2022-04-21|first=Ryan|last=Rocca}}</ref>。她於6月省選中贏取1萬5千多票，當選多倫多中選區省議員<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.elections.on.ca/content/dam/NGW/sitecontent/2022/results/Vote%20Totals%20From%20Official%20Tabulation%20-%20Toronto%20Centre%20109.pdf|title=VOTE TOTALS FROM OFFICIAL TABULATION - 2022 Provincial General Election - Toronto Centre|publisher=安大略選舉局|accessdate=2022-06-22}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.mingpaocanada.com/Tor/htm/News/20220603/tac1_r.htm | title=保守黨3華裔省議員成功連任 黃慧文轉線晉身省議員 徐正陶「華麗回歸」 | date=2022-06-03 | publisher=《明報》加東網 | accessdate=2022-06-22 }}</ref>。

